Oh, hey there, fellas.

20
00:01:25,961 --> 00:01:27,421
Have you by any chance
seen a cool dog

21
00:01:27,462 --> 00:01:29,298
or a giant, smelly lady
come through here?

22
00:01:29,339 --> 00:01:30,841
[Claws clicking]

23
00:01:33,468 --> 00:01:37,097
Uh, are you guys being weird,
or is that normal crab stuff?

24
00:01:37,097 --> 00:01:38,932
[Clicking]

25
00:01:38,974 --> 00:01:40,601
Stupid crabs.

26
00:01:44,563 --> 00:01:46,064
[Plunk!]

27
00:01:46,106 --> 00:01:47,566
[Wind howling]

28
00:01:47,608 --> 00:01:49,359
[Grunts]

29
00:01:51,111 --> 00:01:52,571
Jake?!

30
00:01:52,613 --> 00:01:54,197
Susan?!

31
00:01:56,950 --> 00:01:57,951
Hello?

32
00:02:02,205 --> 00:02:03,749
Burlap sacks.

33
00:02:03,749 --> 00:02:05,751
Seed packets.

34
00:02:07,336 --> 00:02:08,545
Oh.

35
00:02:08,545 --> 00:02:10,005
[Exhales forcefully]

36
